::KitKat::

She looked at Quickstrike.  she sighed and looked at Wildfire.
"OK, I'll help.  I'll show you what happened from my point.  But I'm 
only doing this for my friend. But remember, you harm him in anyway 
and your slag. Got it!"

She sat down her haunches down, and sat upright in wolf mode.  She 
went through her mind from when she first went into the cave to the 
pond, to the tunnel, to finding Quickstrike, to seeing the strange 
wolf bot, to being kicked across the cave, to escaping out of the 
cave.
